Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE in conjunction with Central Commercial Group is pleased to present 2/11 Independent Way, Ravenhall, for sale or lease.
 
The property is located in the thriving Orbis Business Park in Ravenhall, approximately 2.5kms* from the Western Freeway.
 
The Orbis Estate is home to blue chip occupiers such as Fuji Xerox, AS Colour, Flavorite Foods, United Foods as well as the popular Eating Station Café, Kool Kidz Childcare and is less than 100 metres from the IGA Supermarket and United Petrol Station.
 
Alarm system, security roller shutters, structured cabling for phone and internet, separate server room, high-end office finishes and modern façade makes this a easy choice for any business looking for a contemporary office warehouse which allows you to walk in and immediately start operating.
 
The property's location will be positively impacted by the Robinsons Road upgrade in the coming years with improved road access that will benefit logistics occupiers. Further enhancing the sites location is the proximity to the Robinsons Road interchange offering direct access to the Western Freeway and Western Ring Road both within a mere 2 kilometres of the site.
 
Key property features include:
+ Office area over two levels with multiple split systems
+ High clearance clear span warehouse with great natural light
+ Bathroom with shower
+ Separate kitchen area
+ Large open plan first floor office
+ Secure yard with concrete hardstand area of 320sqm*
+ Electronic gate access
+ 9 car spaces
+ Building area: 691sqm*
+ Secure yard of 320sqm*
+ Air-conditioned office over two levels

Please contact the conjunctional agents from CBRE and Central Commercial Group for further information.

The property is currently tenanted by Agru Australia who commenced operation in 1990 and is a renowned supplier of high quality plastic products in the Australian market.

Over the past 30 + years, Agru has grown to be a major distributor of innovative plastic products including fittings, pipes, industrial piping systems, semi-finished products, concrete protection and liners.
